---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy settings and analytics disclosure">
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy and analytics</h1>
    <p>
      We use Google Analytics only when you explicitly allow it. This page explains what we track,
      why we track it, and how to update your consent choices at any time.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>Provider</h2>
      <p>Google Analytics is our analytics provider.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Purpose</h2>
      <p>
        We use aggregate visit measurement to understand which pages are used and improve public
        synthesis readability over time.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What we track</h2>
      <p>When consent is granted, analytics may record:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Page path visited</li>
        <li>Visit timestamp</li>
        <li>Basic device/browser information</li>
        <li>Pageview event</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>How to change consent</h2>
      <p>
        Use the <strong>Privacy settings</strong> link in the footer on any page to reopen consent
        controls and update your choice immediately.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have privacy or technical questions, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:privacy@scipop.org">privacy@scipop.org</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
